{"tid":2057484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報：一年動盪共產黨忍夠了 純潔的知識青年勿再被反共派蒙蔽利用","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:04:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a53c22cc238892dae381e46db3c7a394f05eee14","tid":2057484,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:50:08.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》：港區國安法為香港走出困局帶來希望<br />\n2020-06-09 HKT 19:02<br />\n<br />\n今日是本港反修例示威一周年，民陣表示除七一遊行外，亦計劃舉行反「港區國安法」集會。內地《環球時報》發表社評，形容過去一年動盪重傷香港，「港區國安法」為香港走出困局帶來希望，沒有力量能夠阻止國安法的制定和頒佈實施。<br />\n<br />\n社評指，港區國安法在香港仍有一段時間落實，部分「賣港賣國分子」驚慌利用這段時間頑抗掙扎，全力煽動市民，希望香港不諳世事的年輕學生切勿再被他們蒙蔽利用，又指極端勢力囂張了一年已經「夠了」。<br />\n<br />\n社評強調香港反對派與英美政府想定義「一國兩制」、「高度自治」，是對《基本法》的褻瀆，香港社會須與國家一起邁出一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531113-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531113-20200609.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XeltHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=911124af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531113-20200609.htm&h=7bcf1945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531113-20200609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"43a9af72b046295c3f34077f6875d2c50dc2fd87","tid":2057484,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"繼續作最後嘅鳩叫啦，邪惡組織收皮在即，真係大快人心"},{"pid":"612bea9d63f1ebffa90ab3f40bd0311cae6f5623","tid":2057484,"uid":42804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一味製造稻草人，明明係保衛家園，卻被侵略者講成破壞家園。"},{"pid":"239ff817c83a490cd853e8a41ed8d7673d91c5c4","tid":2057484,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"想黎多次六四?"},{"pid":"40e619ff8a497538e743d9c99a96416d34688cc8","tid":2057484,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"主人都未出聲，走狗就忍唔住衝出黎吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236e0e27d7d9fcde28c0f817d53e3ad7b88b04e7","tid":2057484,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"吳小姐明明話要放棄"}]}